&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a&lt;strong&gt; Strategic Enterprise Sales Director&lt;/strong&gt; to lead high-value, multi-million-dollar deals with global enterprise companies. This role is ideal for a consultative sales leader with a &lt;strong&gt;deep understanding of complex enterprise sales, strategic account planning, and MEDDICC methodology&lt;/strong&gt;. You will be responsible for developing and executing long-term account strategies that drive revenue growth and deepen customer relationships.&lt;/p&gt;
