&lt;li&gt;Present &lt;strong&gt;business cases and ROI models&lt;/strong&gt; to justify investment in our solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop deep industry expertise to &lt;strong&gt;anticipate market trends and customer needs&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive &lt;strong&gt;thought leadership&lt;/strong&gt; by participating in key industry events and conferences.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
