&lt;li&gt;Exceptional &lt;strong&gt;strategic thinking, problem-solving, and negotiation skills&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable working with &lt;strong&gt;cross-functional teams&lt;/strong&gt; to drive enterprise adoption.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Background in &lt;strong&gt;AI, cybersecurity, identity, analytics, or infrastructure SaaS&lt;/strong&gt; is highly preferred.&lt;/li&gt;
